* Episode 34: {{Cite news|first=Karen|last=Ressler|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-09-07/japan-animation-tv-ranking-august-28-september-3/.121078|title=Japan's Animation TV Ranking, August 28 – September 3|work=[[Anime News Network]]|date=September 7, 2017|access-date=October 2, 2017|archive-date=October 2, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171002232301/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-09-07/japan-animation-tv-ranking-august-28-september-3/.121078|url-status=live}}
