* {{Cite web|last=Loo|first=Egan|title=Top-Selling Media Franchises in Japan: 2017|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-12-23/top-selling-media-franchises-in-japan-2017/.125682|website=[[Anime News Network]]|date=December 23, 2017|access-date=August 3, 2022|archive-date=June 1, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220601014918/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-12-23/top-selling-media-franchises-in-japan-2017/.125682|url-status=live}}
